Ipinapalagay na si Zhang, na

00:36:19.840 --> 00:36:20.720
naging ama lang

00:36:20.720 --> 00:36:21.400
at kailangang nasa bahay.

00:36:21.760 --> 00:36:22.800
Ang iba, matanda man,

00:36:23.120 --> 00:36:24.040
o may mga anak na kasama

00:36:24.040 --> 00:36:25.040
malalaking pagsusulit ang paparating.

00:36:25.040 --> 00:36:25.840
Hindi nila ito kayang takpan.

