Ang iba naman ay may lugar na mapaglalaruan.

00:39:45.200 --> 00:39:46.320
Bakit ayaw mo?

00:39:47.160 --> 00:39:48.240
Nahuhuli,

00:39:48.240 --> 00:39:48.920
katulad ko lang?

